  <div class="content clear-block">
    <h1 class="blog-section-title"><a href="/kevin-drum" title="Kevin Drum Blog Index">Kevin Drum</a></h1><span class="prev-next-header"><a href="/kevin-drum/2015/02/friday-cat-blogging-6-february-2015">Previous</a> | <a href="/kevin-drum/2015/02/what-do-americas-most-admired-men-and-women-say-about-america">Next</a></span>  </div>

  
