    <div id="subform_fund" class="biz relative">
    <h3 class="special_relay spring_fundraising_15">
    SPRING FUNDRAISING DRIVE
    </h3>
    <p><em>Mother Jones</em> is a nonprofit, and we need to raise $150,000 by April 30.  The majority of our funding comes from readers like you&#8212;and that keeps us free, independent, and uncensored.<p>
    <p>Please make your tax-deductible gift today.</p>

